11:40 PM - To night was the saddest night ever.... 
Current mood:  sad 


Tonight was the fucking saddest night ever. I went to the SPOM with Sarah, Chrissy and Evangeline and just so much stuff happened and all that made me so fucking sad.
So here it goes.
My dad dropped us off and we walk down to the enterance and decide to walk to shelby farms...anyway we're leaving and I see this guy that I liked SO fucking much and shit, and he just kinda looked at me and I did the same and didn't do anything. That was fucking sad. The one time I see him, he fucking hates me. I was about to cry. 
We come back and we're standing at the first stage and people are moshing and shit and I see him, and i'm just looking and I told Chrissy about it and she did like a sad AW face and It made me so angry with myself and him. 
Then we decided to sit on the ramp and he kept moving and shit and walked past us maybe 2 times and then moved to the crowd that was close to us then just left.
It was so fucking horrible. Then we went to watch the fireworks and we all we're saying how lonely and how this guy chrissy was suppose to met and shit wasn't there or we didn't see him and it made me feel so bad. 

I have no idea why I wanted to tell you guys, but it just made me feel like I have no one that loves me as much as he said he did. 
He was the best thing to me then it just went away.

wow i hate to type a lot at 2:21am, but i must share my expierence of my first 2 days of music fest so far. Ok, so on Friday, it fuckin poured, we got wet, we saw people we knew and Switchfoot was fuckin amazing. Chrissy bawled, i teared up and wow. They spoke about life and it was just so beautiful.

Earlier today when we got there we got there at about 5 or whatever, there were so many fuckin people and it was muddy and disgusting as hell. & everyone was getting drunk and stoned,buy pipes, and necklaces with weed or stuff like that. So we went to see Collective Soul so we could hang out and be pretty close and stay their for Corssfade and the Killerz...wow did that suck. If it had been like the crowd on Friday, i woulda been all YAY! & hibbie gibbie stuff, but NO. Everyone for some fuckin odd reason kept coming. Sarah, Chrissy, Claire and myself were right by this gate that goes around the stage, & it turned out we were where the "door" was. HOLY FUCK THAT WAS STUPID. All these people came through, and were leaving, i didn't even know who the fuck Collective Soul was until we left. So first thing I see is a guy in a parachute...riiiighhttt, someone says its the lead singer and then i'm like wow landed pa retty far away. Then some chick says that he smacked some 18 year old girl over there & that's why it was takin so long, and all this shit, sayin they canceled. So we're waiting, pepople are pushin,shoving, movin,yellin and fuckin gropin us. I have never been touched that much in a period of 20 minutes in my life by absolute strangers. Finally, Collective Soul comes on & more people are goin and comin which i'm wonderin why they're leavin, and someone said cuz of the mosh pit which i was about to be all over like lines or ruled notebook paper. We saw people gettin kicked out for surfing or whatever it's called...cough retards cough. Then there came this lady who looked like she was with her teenage girl, who looked like the one that got kicked in the face, so they music was goin and that lady was wipin the girls face lookin like she was tryin to make her happy...NO. ABSO FRICKIN LUTELY NOT. They were both so fuckin high & drunk i don't think they even heard the music or anything else, kinda like when you laugh extremely hard and you kinda lose your hearin during the brief moment. Then it becomes fuckin gammed back, and Claire hit the gate cuz we were bored then 20 or 30 minutes later the security guard who looked like Santa Clause, pushed the gate with all his might from the other side movin us the crowd into each other when we had no fuckin room. then he did it again! so the lady who i thought was the mom pushes back and she was really weird & was dancin and grindin with Claire cuz that's how little room we had so he took her and i was kidna relieved then all these peopel kept comin so i was like fuck i can't be this close to pot smokin drunk stragners so i pushed Claire and we pused through people to get some room. It was so fuckin scary. I mean I don't wanna sound like a weiner and all, but I mean i've seen people go down in crowds and not get back up. During this there is this pretty damn fi0ne blonde haired guy right behind Chrissy and next to Claire& kept watchin me and stuff and laughin at what we were sayin that made me glad. So many guys, drunk & not, hit on us. Wow, i love it. :D When Sarah &  i got seperated from Claire & Chrissy, we were walkin through the clothin area and this guy looks and me and i smile then i moved my hair, & since it had rained the night before i had to try my jacket in Sarah's dryer so it kinda shrunk and so my jacket went up and he goes DUH AM & then i look at him and he goes YOU'RE FUCKIN SEXY AS HELL then i looked back at him and walked away. The night before made me the happiest, so we all are walkin, soaked, to Claire's car, when these 2 guys in the street walk past us, Chrissy is behind me, so they walk past me and I look and kinda smile then they walk past Chrissy then Chrissy comes up to me and says Alexis, those guys said to tell you, you were hot. I was like yes yay feel gorgeous so i scream Thank you & they look back & smile So Chrissy is just sayin how he walked past her & said that they wanted her to tell moi, their friend, i was hot. then I scream again I LOVE YOU SWEETHEART & that was it basically that happened at Music Fest that was interesingly big and shocking! Well, i gotta go and get some sleep BILLY IDOL & CHEVELLE are tomorrow, i think i'm only goin with chrissy, definatley, that I know of.
